@startuml 12-memory-projection
title Memory Projection — 64^n Resident Universe

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

component "64^2 attention memory\n4,096 bits = 512 B\n(where dteam should look)" as Att
component "64^3 active universe\n262,144 bits = 32 KiB\nUniverseBlock = [u64; 4096]\n(what is currently true)" as Active
component "64^4 meaning field\n16,777,216 bits = 2 MiB\n(law / risk / reward /\n scenario / projection planes)" as Meaning

component "dteam attention cells\n(focus set)" as AttCells
component "dteam process truth\n(route / state / control)" as Truth
component "dteam semantic planes\n(law, reward, risk, scenario, projection)" as Planes

component "dteam UProjection\n(verified human-readable view)" as Projection

Att --> AttCells : projection rule π_att
Active --> Truth : projection rule π_active
Meaning --> Planes : projection rule π_meaning

AttCells --> Projection
Truth --> Projection
Planes --> Projection

note bottom of Projection
  UProjection is not authority.
  Authority is ΔU + UReceipt.
  Projections are disposable
  (dteam_receipt + regenerate).
end note

@enduml
